0198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"59302357b007c88b0f7946e26ef4df088d16b6ee","tid":1631650,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7e05dab2d4a812579746a10655c3ba9d151e53ac","tid":1631650,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"裝修商鋪係好有用<br />\n商界一直企係強權果邊或者食花生姿態<br />\n終於發現到事態嚴重<br />\n因為只要你要係香港做生意<br />\n就冇辦法唔理民意<br />\n<br />\n政府都一樣<br />\n香港本身嘅和平繁榮係靠香港人合作同妥協換返黎<br />\n香港人都可以選擇唔合作唔妥協<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw勇武不嬲係智商高d果班黎..."},{"pid":"7970cf8d364aee911e9d5ceafdaff443d05ebd1a","tid":1631650,"uid":50848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e09b8cd12600451d2042344035ab27f9e50297ec","tid":1631650,"uid":238497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:05:5